Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US-China relations
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wq0w
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 13 Dec 1981
West Coast view of China leads to double standard over question of dissidents in Communist states. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less